Kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) bwazamutse cyane mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi (EEA) ndetse no mu Bwongereza.
Ikigaragaza ko ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) bwiyongereye mu bihugu byose, byerekana ko hari ibintu bisa mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ibihugu bihana imbibi n'u Bwongereza, kandi ko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera cyane mu bihugu byose, mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'igihugu.
Ishingiye ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kongera ubushishozi mu guhangana n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habaye icyorezo cy'uburwayi bw'ibicurane mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, kitaramenyekana impamvu yabyo.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko cyatoye ikintu cyateje icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya, ubu cyitwa coronavirus ikomeye yo mu buhumekero 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yitwa icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibipimo byerekana ko hafi 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bahindutse impumyi, ariko ntibahinduke impumyi cyangwa se bakagira ubwandu bworoheje bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu byorezo bigera kuri 14%, COVID-19 yateye indwara ikomeye cyane ikeneye kuvurirwa mu bitaro, naho mu byorezo bikurikiyeho 6%, habonetse uburwayi bukomeye bukeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abapfa mu gihe bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, tugiye gusuzuma ibyago byo gukwirakwira kwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, tugereranyije n'u Bushinwa n'intara ya Hubei.
Twagereranyije kandi imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) n'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EEA) n'ubw'u Bwongereza n'ubw'u Butaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Nyuma yo gutangira mu Bushinwa, COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu tundi turere, ndetse n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye imbere mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi cyasohotse ku wa 5 Werurwe, Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. cyatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe bwa mbere mu bantu bo mu Burayi, hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'icyorezo cya OMS.
Abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye muri EU/EEA babonetse mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020, bakaba bari bavuye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ibihugu 30 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi (EU) /umuryango w'ubukungu w'Uburayi (EEA) n'ubwongereza byatangaje ko byibasiye COVID-19, aho mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 habayeho abantu 39,768 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye bagera ku 1,727, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine habayeho abantu 17,750 banduye ndetse n'abapfuye bagera ku 1,441.
Gutanga imibare y'ibyangijwe na COVID-19 n'umubare w'ibyangijwe
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) gisubiza amakuru ku mibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo, bivuye mu nzego z'ubuzima, mu nzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere, ndetse n'ibikoresho byemewe n'amategeko nka OMS.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, no kugereranya imimerere y'ibihugu byombi n'iy'u Butaliyani.
Kugira ngo tumenye uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongeye gukwirakwira, twakoze ibarura ry'ibimenyetso by'uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongeye gukwirakwira mu minsi 14 yose mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, kandi dukoresheje ibipimo bisanzwe bya COVID-19.
Turatangaza kandi umubare w'ubwandu bwagaragaye mu gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'igitondo, ugereranyije n'ubwandu bwagaragaye mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibibazo by'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Ibipimo by'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi (EEA) n'u Bwongereza, mu by'ukuri ni kimwe n'ibipimo by'ubwiyongere bw'ubwiyongere mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, icyiciro cy'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 cyatangiye kuzamuka ahagana ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho kigera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Icyiciro cy'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'ubwandu bw'icyorezo cya COVID-19 bwagaragaye mu Butaliyani, ndetse n'ubwiyongere nk'ubwo mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Area économique européenne (EEA) ndetse n'u Bwongereza (amakuru y'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigereranya umubare wiyongereye wa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza 15 Werurwe 2020 n'umubare w'abandura mu Butaliyani.
Nyuma y'ibyumweru bitatu n'ibyumweru bike, ibihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi (EU) /umuryango w'ubukungu w'Uburayi (EEA) n'Ubwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye muri icyo gihugu ugereranywa n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani, ku isaha ya saa munani z'igitondo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza uri kwiyongera cyane.
Ibitekerezo by'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 byakurikiranwe byerekana ko icyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera ku kigero kimwe mu bihugu byose.
Imikorere y'ubuzima rusange mu bihugu bitandukanye iri mu byiciro bitandukanye, mu byiciro bitandukanye, kandi ikomeje kugenda itandukana bitewe n'igihugu mu buryo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa COVID-19, harimo ibipimo by'icyorezo n'ibipimo by'ubushakashatsi.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'ubutaliyani byibasiwe na COVID-19 bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi cyane muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku gipimo cyo hejuru cy'abarwayi.
Ku rwego rw'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) /Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi (EEA), 6% na 1% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye ni byo byonyine biboneka (amakuru ntabwo agaragajwe).
Ariko, kugira ngo dukomeze kugenzura amakuru ariho, yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye, tugomba kubasaba ko bakorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwerekanye ko umubare w'ibitaro by'indembe mu Burayi n'iby'indembe bihinduka cyane bitewe n'igihugu, aho mu Budage hari ibitaro 29.2 ku bantu 100.000, mu gihe muri Portugal hari ibitaro 4.2 gusa.
Ibi bivuze ko bashobora kuba bafite umutungo munini ariko kandi ari muto ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (umubare w'ibitanda byo kwita ku barwayi b'indwara z'uburwayi bukomeye n'uburwayi bwo mu rwego ruciriritse ku bantu 100.000 mu mwaka wa 2010-2011).
Ibipimo by'ibimenyetso by'ibyago by'uburwayi byerekeranye no kugabanyuka kw'ubwisungane mu kwivuza byashyizwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'icyerekezo cy'ibyago bya COVID-19 cya ECDC, hamwe n'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro byerekana ko abarwayi bafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe bashobora kurenga 90% by'abarwayi bashobora kuvurwa mu buvuzi bw'ibanze mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza.
