Iyo icyorezo kidashobora kugenzurwa, hakwiye gufatwa ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka zacyo ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Imikorere yo kugabanya no gukumira ishobora gukoreshwa icyarimwe.
Kugira ngo icyorezo cy'icyorezo kigabanuke ku isi, hakenewe ingamba zikomeye zo kugabanya ubwandu bwo hasi ya 1. Ni mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubwandu bwo mu gihe cy'ibihe by'icyorezo, nk'igice cyo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Ibi bishobora kugabanya ibyago byo gukwirakwiza serivisi z'ubuzima kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe kinini cyo gushaka imiti n'uburyo bwo kuvura.
Ingamba z'ubuvuzi n'izitazibagirana zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo zirimo isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwitandukanya, ingamba z'ubutabazi bwite zigamije kugabanya imikoranire y'abantu nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro rusange, ibikorwa by'ubufatanye by'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibikorwa byavuzwe haruguru, no kwirinda ubwandu mu bidukikije nko kwirinda ubwandu mu Bushinwa.
Mu bindi bihugu, hashyizweho ingamba zitandukanye mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangiye gupima abantu benshi no kubacungira ahantu hamwe, kandi itanga imiburo kubijyanye n'aho abantu banduye bajya.
Singapore iha inkunga y'amafaranga abantu banduye kandi bakigenzura, kandi igahana amafaranga menshi ku batabikora.
Tayiwani yongereye inganda zikora udupfukamunwa no gupfuka mu maso, kandi ifata ingamba zo kubika ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ibipimo bisa n'ibyo mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika byerekana ko hari imbogamizi zikomeye mu kugabanya ubwandu (gukora ku buryo butinda gusa, aho guhagarika ikwirakwira) no kugabanya ubwandu (guhindura umuvuduko w'icyorezo).
Amategeko yo kugabanya ubukana ashobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa ugera kuri bibiri bya gatatu by'abapfa, ariko ubuzima bugomba kuba bugenda nabi, kandi abantu ibihumbi amagana baracyapfa.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya ubwandu bushobora kuba bukomeye, ariko mu gihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage, iyo ingamba zisuzuguritse (iyo umuti wa mbere wabonetse), ubwandu bushobora kongera kwiyongera vuba, bityo bigasaba ko habaho ibikorwa byo kugabanya ubwandu.
Gucunga iki cyorezo bisaba ingamba z'igihe kirekire kandi bishobora guteza ingaruka zikomeye mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Kugeza ubu nta muti wihariye wa COVID-19 uraboneka, ariko hari ibikorwa byinshi birimo gukorwa, harimo no kugerageza imiti iriho.
Gufata imiti igabanya ubukana bw'ibicurane, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Ukurikije ubukana bw'ubwandu, umuntu ashobora gukenera ko afata imiti ya oxygénothérapie, imiti yo guhumeka no gukoresha imashini ifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu akoresheje ibiyobyabwenge, bishobora gutuma arushaho kugira ingaruka mbi.
Hari imiti myinshi yemewe gukoreshwa mu kuvura izindi ndwara za virusi irimo kugeragezwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga kandi ko uburyo gakondo bwo kuvura no kuvura mu rugo bishobora koroshya ibimenyetso by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-19.
OMS yavuze ko kuzamura ubushobozi no guhindura uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima hakurikijwe ibyo abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ari imwe mu ngamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ibiro by'akarere bya OMS na ECDC byasohoye amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze, kugira ngo bihindure umutungo mu byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gupima ibizamini bya laboratwari byo gupima COVID-19, guhagarika uburyo bwo gutora, gushyira mu kato no gushyira mu kato abarwayi ba COVID-19, kongera ubushobozi bw'abakozi mu kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19, no kongera umubare w'imiti n'ibikoresho byo guhumeka byihutirwa.
Hariho ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku byerekeye aho umurwayi wa mbere (witwa umurwayi wa 0) atangirira.
Igihe icyorezo cya coronavirus cyamenyekanaga bwa mbere, gishobora gukurikiraho ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus mu mujyi wa Hubei wariyongereye cyane.
Abenshi muri bo bafitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibiribwa by'ibinyabuzima, aho n'inyamaswa zibayeho zigurishwa, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora kuba yaturutse ku nyamaswa cyangwa se ko ishobora kuba ari yo yavuye ku nyamaswa igakwirakwira ku bantu.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan babwiye bagenzi babo ko bafite ubwoko bwa coronavirus bufite inkomoko ya SARS.
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang bahawe umuburo n'abapolisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, undi ni Ai Fen, wahawe umuburo ukomeye n'abayobozi be kubera ko yatumye habaho imvururu.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan nyuma yasohoye itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Ukuboza, kandi imenyesha OMS.
Nyuma yo kubona amakuru ahagije ku cyorezo cya pneumonia itamenyekanye, abayobozi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan batangiye gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Kubera ko Wuhan ari ikigo cy'itumanaho kandi ari umuhanda munini w'imodoka, hamwe n'ingendo zo mu mwaka w'ubukwe w'Abashinwa, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020.
Kugeza ku wa 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abantu 140 banduye, barimo babiri muri Beijing n'umwe muri Shenzhen.
Nyuma y'aho, amakuru yemewe yagaragaje ko abantu 6,174 bagaragaje ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zagiye zirenga Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mwanya w'ibihugu bifite umubare munini w'abamaze kwandura. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose hatangajwe ko hari abantu miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kwandura, abantu 97,000 bapfuye, abandi barenga 364,000 barakira.
Mu gihugu no mu ntara zigera kuri 200, nibura hari umuntu umwe wanduye.
Mu Burayi, icyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen bigabanya urujya n'uruza rw'abantu, ndetse no kugabanya imipaka.
Ingamba ku rwego rw'igihugu zirimo ingamba zo kwirinda ingendo (izitwa kandi Guma mu Rugo, Guma mu Rugo cyangwa Guma mu Rugo) n'amabwiriza yo kutagira aho bava. Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, ni ukuvuga 90% by'abaturage bo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, barenga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine, barenga miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo na miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde, bari mu kato.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari bafite ubumuga runaka, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri bukwira bukagera kuri miliyari 2.6 (ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi).
Umuntu wa mbere wafashwe na COVID-19 yagaragaye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, amakuru atazwi avuga ko icyorezo cya mbere cyabaye ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yagaragaye ko afite icyorezo cy'uburwayi bw'ibicurane ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi ubwo yagaragaye ko afite uburwayi, yahise abimenyesha Wuhan Jainghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, ibipimo bya mbere byagenewe mu buryo bw'imiterere y'umuntu byagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'ubuyobozi bwa Wuhan yasohoye umuburo ku baturage ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
Ku munsi w'ejo, WHO yabimenyeshejwe.
Nubwo izi mburi zatanzwe, abapolisi baburiye abaganga bo muri Wuhan kubera ibihuha bakwirakwiza ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta gihamya ifatika y'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, Xi Jinping, nyuma yaho yashyizeho gahunda nini yo guhashya ikwirakwira rya virusi, iyo guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yise intambara y'abaturage.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, leta ya Hong Kong yahagaritse by'agateganyo ingendo zijya no kwinjira mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu byo yahishuye ko ari cyo gikorwa gikomeye cyo kugenzura abantu mu mateka, byongere bigera mu mijyi 15 mu ntara ya Hubei, bigira ingaruka ku bantu miliyoni 57.
Mu mujyi wa Kigali, imodoka zigomba guhagarara.
Mu bice byinshi, ibirori by'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (byagombaga kuba ku wa 25 Mutarama) byarahagaritswe.
Abayobozi batangaje ko barimo kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo bya Huoshenshan, bizarangira mu minsi 10.
Ibitaro bya Leishenshan byubatswe, ikindi bitaro, kugirango haboneke abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, indi nyubako 14 nka Convention Center na Sitade i Wuhan, zakoreshejwe nk'ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi gahunda zirimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kongera iminsi mikuru y'umunsi w'impeshyi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Mu gihugu hose, amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe.
Mu karere ka Hong Kong na Macau, hashyizweho gahunda n'ibindi bikorwa by'ubwubatsi, by'umwihariko ku mashuri, za kaminuza.
Mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa, uburyo bwo gukora mu buryo bwa kure bwatangiye gukoreshwa.
Mu gihe cy'ibiganiro by'umushyikirano, Perezida Kagame yavuze ko hari abantu benshi batitabiriye inama y'umushyikirano.
Mu gihugu hose, ibikorwa byo kuvugurura imodoka za Leta n'amazu ndangamurage byafunzwe byamaze igihe.
Gucunga ingendo rusange birakorwa mu mijyi myinshi, aho abaturage bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage bose) bafite uburyo runaka bwo guhagarika kuva mu rugo. Icyorezo cyageze ku rwego rw'icyorezo ku isi muri Werurwe, kandi abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi z'ibindi bihugu zinjira mu gihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku bantu bose binjira mu mujyi, iminsi itanu mbere y'uko hashyirwaho iryo tegeko, ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa hari umuntu umwe wanduye, wanduye umukozi w'ingenzi wari uvuye i Istanbul mu mujyi wa Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko icyorezo cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa kandi ko cyafashwe.
Nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gufunga ingendo z'abanyamahanga, ku munsi umwe gusa, uretse Wuhan, Hubei na yo yahishuye ko ihagaritse gahunda yo kugenzura ingendo. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko ihagaritse abemerewe kwinjira cyangwa gutura kuva ku wa 28 Werurwe, ariko ntiyavuga igihe nyacyo iyi gahunda izarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa mu biro by'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi n'inganda byongera gufungura ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, itanga inkunga y'amafaranga yo gukomeza ibikorwa. Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye abaganga b'imiryango gukora imihango yo kwibuka ku buryo buhoraho kuri interineti, bakurikije gahunda yo kwirinda gukwirakwiza icyorezo cya COVID-19, ariko Inama Njyanama y'Intara yatangaje ko ku munsi umwe n'umunsi mukuru wa Kung Fu ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri, hazabaho iminota itatu yo guceceka ku rwego rw'igihugu, ari na yo izaba ari intangiriro y'icyunamo.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, Koreya y'Epfo yemeje ko ifite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwandujwe mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ku wa 20 Gashyantare ko umubare w'abanduye wazamutse cyane, abenshi muri bo bakaba banduye mu gihe bari bateraniye mu kigo cya Daegu cy'ishyaka rishya ry'idini ryitwa Shinchongi Church of Jesus Christ.
Abashumba ba Shincheonji bari mu rugendo baturutse i Wuhan bajya i Daegu muri Koreya y'Epfo, bakekwaho kuba ari bo batangije icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, 1,261 mu bayoboke 9,336 b'itorero, cyangwa 13%, bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko igipimo cyo hejuru cy'ububisha cyabaye ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Muri Koreya, abamaze kwemezwa ko banduye ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare barenga 2,000, ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare bagera ku 3150.
Nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basuzumwe basanga banduye virusi, ibiro bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byose byashyizwe mu kato.
Korea y'Epfo yatangije gahunda ya mbere yo gupima abantu no gutandukanya abanduye, gukurikirana abo bahuye nabo no kubacungira ukwa bonyine, icyo kikaba ari cyo gikorwa kinini kandi cyiza ku isi.
Uburyo bwo gupima burimo gutangaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ku bantu baba mu ngendo mpuzamahanga no kugaruka, hakoreshejwe porogaramu ya terefone igendanwa, gupima virusi mu ngendo no gutanga amakuru nyuma y'umunsi ukurikiyeho, kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20,000 buri munsi.
Ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu mu mujyi wose wa Koreya y'Epfo, aho guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wose, zishobora gufatwa nk'iz'ibyiza.
Mu gihe hari abantu benshi bo muri Koreya bavuga ko leta itari ifite ubushobozi bwo gukemura ikibazo cy'icyorezo, hari n'abashyigikiye ko Moon akurwaho n'ibisubizo bye.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje umubare muto w'abanduye umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abanyamahanga bose bashya bazajya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 1 Mata, ikinyamakuru kimwe cyatangaje ko Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ubufasha bwo gupima virusi mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Umurwayi wa mbere wa SARS-CoV-2 mu gihugu cya Irani wavuye mu mujyi wa Quang, watangajwe ku ya 19 Gashyantare, kandi abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'uwo munsi nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi ibivuga.
Ingamba za mbere zafashwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco, imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari eshanu z'amadolari ya Irani mu kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rohini yatangaje ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira abantu mu kato, ko abantu ari bo bonyine bagomba kujya mu kato.
Nubwo imodoka nyinshi zinyura mu mijyi mbere ya Nowrouz y'umwaka mushya wa Arabiya Sawudite, muri Werurwe hatangajwe gahunda zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi.
Amasinagogi ya Shiite muri Qom muri Irani yakomeje gufungurirwa abagenzi kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu gihe hari ibirego by'uko umubare w'abandura muri Irani wahishwe, ibihugu birenga icumi byongeye kugaragara ko ubwandu mu bihugu byabo bufitanye isano na Irani mbere ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko ushobora kuba ufite ubwandu bukomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yatangaje kuri iyo tariki.
Ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yahagaritse ibikorwa byayo nyuma y'uko 23 mu badepite 290 bagaragaye ko banduye virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu Human Rights Watch wasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani gufungura burundu abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira kutumvikana mu mahoro, no gufungura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifungiwe muri gereza.
Ibigo by'abarwayi bifunze, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije, nk'ibigo by'impunzi, bishobora guteza ubwandu bwa virusi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yavuze ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari na bwo bushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko ari bwo bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko abantu benshi bapfuye muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, mu gihugu cya Irani, abantu bagera kuri 12 bishwe n'ibisasu by'ibisasu by'ubumara.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yabonye abantu bashya 50 buri saha n'urupfu buri minota 10 bishwe na coronavirus.
Abategetsi ba OMS bavuga ko muri Irani, umubare w'abandura ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu ugereranyije n'uko byatangajwe.
Ibihugu by'Abasoviyeti byashyize imbere uburyo bwo kwinjiza amafaranga mu gihugu, ariko byanze bikunze byatangiye kwibasirwa n'ibihe bibi.
Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye y'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyakomeje kwiyongera mu Butaliyani ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwe ko banduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma ku ya 31 Mutarama.
Kubera ubwiyongere bukabije bw'ubwandu, leta y'Ubutaliyani yahagaritse ingendo z'indege z'indege n'iz'ingenzi z'u Bushinwa ndetse itangaza ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukene.
Icyorezo cy'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 cyatangiye ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, aho abantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye mu mujyi wa Labardi. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, inama y'abaminisitiri yasohoye itegeko ryo kugenzura ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, harimo no gushyira abantu barenga 50,000 mu kato mu mijyi 11 yo mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani.
Minisitiri w'intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko nta muntu wemerewe kwinjira cyangwa gusohoka mu duce dufite icyorezo.
"Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri na kaminuza bifungwa mu gihugu hose, kuko mu Butaliyani hamaze gupfa abantu bagera ku 100.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, imikino yose yahagaritswe nibura ukwezi kumwe, nubwo imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'umupira w'amaguru, yagombaga gukinwa kugeza muri Mata.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarara, usibye amaduka manini n'amavuriro. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi, Amarozi n'Ubuvuzi bw'Ubutabazi bw'Igihe (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama z'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'ubuvuzi bw'indwara z'ingenzi, zigomba gukurikizwa.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwari bufite abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize ubwandu, buza gusumba Ubushinwa mu kugira umubare munini w'abapfuye bazira coronavirus ku isi.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko indege icyenda z'ingabo z'Uburusiya zoherejwe mu Butaliyani zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Mu gihe mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 128,948 banduye, 15,887 bapfuye, naho 21,815 bakira, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Amakuru yatanzwe na CNN agaragaza ko umubare munini w'abapfuye mu Butaliyani waturutse ku mubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru hamwe no kutabona uburyo bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi mu gihe gikwiriye.
Ubwo iyi virusi yatangiraga kugaragara, Ubwongereza bwari bufite ubwigenge bwinshi mu bihugu byibasiwe n'iyo ndwara, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyigeze isaba abaturage bayo gukora ibikorwa byo kwirinda cyangwa kugenzura mu rwego rw'itsinda.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko yahagaritse ingendo zitari ngombwa n'uburyo bwose bwo guhura n'abandi, asaba abantu gukora bavuye mu rugo uko bishoboka kose no kwirinda ibigo by'imyidagaduro, amazu yo kuriramo n'ibikino.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko igiye gufunga mu maguru mashya ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka pub na sitade, no kwishyura abakozi amafaranga agera kuri £2,500 ku kwezi na 80% by'umushahara wabo, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri mu gihe cy'icyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ko hari ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu, guhagarika guteranira hamwe abantu barenga babiri, no guhagarika ingendo no gusohoka hanze.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uko byari bimeze mbere, polisi yashoboye gushyiraho iyo mipaka binyuze mu gucibwa amande no gutandukanya abantu.
Mu gihe cy'ibihe by'ubukungu, ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi byinshi byasabwe gufungwa, uretse ibicuruzwa byose by'inganda, harimo amasoko manini, ibicuruzwa by'imiti, amabanki, ibicuruzwa by'ibikomoka ku bicuruzwa, ibigo by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'imodoka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye wa COVID-19 yemejwe mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika muri leta ya Washington, umugabo wari watashye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama, hashyizweho akanama gashinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus muri White House.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, leta ya Trump yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima rusange, ndetse igashyiraho n'amategeko akumira abagenzi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatangaje ko cyakoze igikoresho cy'igerageza.
Nubwo Amerika yari itinze gukora ibizamini, ntibyari byoroshye kumenya uko icyorezo cyari kimeze icyo gihe.
Ibipimo by'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byatanzwe na leta ya Fédéral muri Gashyantare, byatumye ibipimo bitagenda neza. Ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe n'imiryango itegamiye kuri leta (intiti, amashuri, kaminuza) ntibyemerewe na leta ya Fédéral kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, bityo abaturage basabwa kuba barakoze ibizamini bitarenze mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (byanasabaga kandi ko byemezwa na muganga).
Washington Post ivuga ko kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, muri Amerika hakorwa ibizamini bitarenga 4,000.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hasigaye ibizamini 14,000 byakozwe.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, AP News yatangaje ko abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ya coronavirus bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupimwa, nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Amerika, kuri uyu wa 29 Gashyantare, leta ya Washington yatangaje ko guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, amashuri yo mu gihugu hose afungwa hagati muri Werurwe. Itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zandura bo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College i Londres, ryatanze inama ku byagereranywa n'ingaruka coronavirus nshya ishobora kugira ku gihugu ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryongereraho uburyo bwo kwitegura no gusubiza coronavirus, ritanga miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari y'ubudehe bw'ibanze ku bigo bya leta mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ibigo by'ubucuruzi byashyizeho ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo ku bakozi, guhagarika inama no gushishikariza abakozi gukora bari mu rugo.
Trump yatangaje ku itariki ya 11 y'uku kwezi ko yahagaritse ingendo mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, usibye mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku itariki ya 13 y'uku kwezi kwa gatatu.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongeye kongerera ingamba zo gufunga ingendo mu Bwongereza na Ireland.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu cyose gihagaze mu bihe by'ubukungu bwihuse, bityo amafaranga ya leta ashobora gukoreshwa mu bikorwa byo guhangana n'ibiza.
Kuva ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, muri Amerika hose, ibikorwa byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunzwe cyangwa amasaha y'akazi agabanuka mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, leta zose 50 hamwe n'akarere ka Columbia byemejwe ko byamaze kwandura. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, New York City yatangaje ko hari abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus, umubare urenze uw'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Guverineri wa leta ya Florida ku itariki ya 25 Werurwe yavuze ko kuba abantu benshi bakomeza kwigunga bisa n'ibishoboka kuko umubare w'abandura wikubye kabiri ku munsi wa 2,0 ugera ku munsi wa 4.7.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, i New York City hemejwe ko hari abantu 32,308 banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe ko ari zo zifite umubare munini w'abanduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera igihe cyo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort, bufite ibitanda 1000, bwashyizwe ku butaka bwa New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika, abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24 gusa.
Muri leta ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata, inzu y'Umurenge yahawe igihano kubera ko yafashe ingamba zo kugabanya ibyago, abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi batangaza ko bakwirakwiza virusi, kandi bagasaba ko bashyikirana na biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence mu gutanga amakuru.
Mu gihe Trump yari amaze igihe kirekire ari mu gihugu, hari abantu benshi batangiye gutinya ko ashobora kuzongera kuba Perezida.
Abategetsi bamwe na bamwe b'Amerika n'ibiro ntaramakuru by'Amerika banenze ibyo kwifashisha ibicuruzwa by'ingoboka by'Ubushinwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo gutembera mu kirere kugira ngo hamenyekane aho iki cyorezo cyandukira no guhanura uburyo cyandura, byatangajwe mu kinyamakuru Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Raporo y'Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Urugendo rwo mu Kirere yo mu 2018 igaragaza ko Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ari byo byibasiwe n'abagenzi benshi baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo bivugwa ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane abantu baturutse i Wuhan.
Mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya ikeneye cyane ubwisungane mu kwivuza, ikirwa cya Bali cyahawe ubutumwa bwo gushyiraho ubwisungane mu kwivuza mu bice 20 bya mbere by'ingenzi.
Nubwo nta bimenyetso byinshi by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 biboneka, Australia ivuga ko izashyiraho ingamba zo kugenzura imipaka no guhuza abantu mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, leta ya Australia yatangaje ko ari yo ifite ikibazo cy'umutekano mu binyabuzima.
Kubera ko imodoka z'abantu benshi zikurikiranwa mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro i Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye kwimura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba ambasade mu karere, mu mizo ya mbere bifata indege z'ubwikorezi mu bihugu by'amavuko, byemerewe n'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni byo bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gahunda yo kwimura abaturage babyo.
Pakistan ivuga ko itazakora ibishoboka byose ngo abaturage bayo bari mu Bushinwa bagarurwe.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, leta ya Brazil yashoboye kwimura abantu bane b'Abanyapolonye, Umunyamerika umwe, Umunyarwanda umwe, hamwe n'Abanyamerika 34 cyangwa abagize umuryango wabo.
Mu gihugu cya Brazil, indege ya Brazil yahagaritse urugendo rwayo mbere yo kujya mu gihugu cya Brazil, aho abaturage ba Polonye, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde bavuye mu ndege.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari mu mujyi wa Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi y'umujyi wa Brasilia.
Mu munsi umwe, 215 b'Abanyakanada (176 mu ndege ya mbere ya leta ya Amerika, 39 mu ya kabiri) bari mu byiciro by'abashyitsi mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri, bavuye i Wuhan bajya ku biro by'iperereza bya CFB i Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abakanada 185 ivuye i Wuhan, yageze ku kibuga cya CFB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bohereje abaturage 277 ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyavuguruwe ngo gibe ikigo cy'uburinzi, ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, bamara iminsi 14 ku kirwa.
Indege y'ubutabazi ya Nouvelle Zélande yageze i Auckland ku wa 5 Gashyantare, abari bayirimo (harimo bamwe mu baturage ba Australia n'abandi baturage bo mu bihugu byo mu nyanja ya Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Whamamaroora mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zizavana Abanyamerika mu bwato bw'icyubahiro bwa Diamond Princess, bakajya ahantu heza.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Pricess, yageze mu mujyi wa Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye igikorwa cyo guhungisha abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airlines yari iteguriwe na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo, yazanye abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo mu gihugu.
Ibizamini by'ubuvuzi byakozwe mbere yo kugenda, kandi abaturage bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus barasiwe kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo bamaze gupimwa neza nibo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu.
Nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda, abaturage bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bose b'indege, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, bakoze urugendo rw'iminsi 14 rw'ubwiteganyirize mu kigo cya The Ranch, nta virusi yabonetse.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku wa 5 Gashyantare ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byatanze imfashanyo ku Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa biga muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bavuze ko mu rwego rwo gufatanya mu gutanga imfashanyo mu turere twugarijwe na virusi, mu karere ka Chicago hose, bageze ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku mafaranga 50.000 y'udupfukamunwa twa N95.
"Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya OMS yo gushakisha urukingo no kuvura abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Nk'uko bitangazwa na Ineraksyon, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje mu mujyi wa Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16, byamenyekanye ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku gihugu cya Philippines ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'inkoko rya Singapore ryatangaje ko rizohereza imfashanyo zigera kuri miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Abashinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko izatanga miliyoni 18 z'intoki z'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda 10,000 ya Herz-Metz, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, kandi yiyemeza kongeramo inkunga y'amafaranga y'amadolari y'Amerika miliyoni 100 mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu Butaliyani mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umunyemari Jamma yohereje ibikoresho by'ibizamini miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro yo kurinda 60,000 mu gihugu cya Ethiopia, Addis Ababa, kugira ngo bihabwe Umuryango w'Ubumwe bwa Afurika.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho bya Pima 5000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka, byashyizwe muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze imfashanyo z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge zabo ku bigunira n'ibikoresho by'igerageza byakozwe n'Ubushinwa.
Urugero, muri Espagne, ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa byasubijwe inyuma bifite 30% gusa by'ukuri, mu gihe mu Buholandi, ibikoresho 600,000 byo gupima mu mazuru byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite amakosa byasubijwe inyuma.
Mu Bubiligi, hafashwe udupfukamunwa 100.000 tutari dukwiriye gukoreshwa, twibeshya ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku ruhande rumwe, ibihugu byo muri Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika byakira imfashanyo z'Ubushinwa. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije gahunda yo gutanga imfashanyo z'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yasabye abayobozi b'Ubushinwa gushyiraho gahunda yo kugenzura no kugenzura icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro rikomeye hagati y'abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwa guhisha amakuru mu ibanga mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, bigatuma ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kurwanya indwara bitinda, na leta y'u Bushinwa ikomeje gutanga amakuru agezweho mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa, "mu gihe cy'iki cyorezo, kugira ngo birinde gutungurwa".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo muri Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS, Gordon Gallia, yagize ati "Nta gushidikanya ko atari inama yatanzwe na OMS". Yavuze ko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cy'ubushake bwo kugenzura icyorezo aho abantu benshi bahurira, avuga ko ari icyorezo kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'abantu.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Edhanouang, yavuze ko itangazo rya PHEIC "rifite ingaruka ku kaga ko kuba icyorezo cyakwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ibifite amikoro yo hagati, bidafite sisitemu nziza y'ubuzima".
Tedros yasubije ku byemezo by'ingendo avuga ko nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitagomba kwivanga mu ngendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi, avuga ko OMS idashyigikira ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi bigabanywa.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira imyiteguro ya strategiki mu bihugu bikennye, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu bitagira uburyo bwo kumenya abanduye virusi, nubwo haba hari icyorezo cya Ebola.
Tedros yasohoye itangazo rivuga ko "dushobora gukomera gusa ku gice cyacu cyoroheje", asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi, cyangwa ikindi gihe igiciro kizaba kinini". Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yahaye izina ry'indwara ya COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'umuryango w'abibumbye wose" mu bikorwa byo gusubiza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Iterambere ryashyizweho, rituma igisubizo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye cyose gihuza. Ibihugu bigize OMS byemerewe kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe ibindi bigo bifasha mu kwihanganira ingaruka zikomeye z'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere byatewe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'abakozi ba WHO riyobowe n'u Bushinwa ryashyizweho, kandi impuguke mpuzamahanga na OMS ku butaka zashyizweho kugirango zifashe Ubushinwa mu gucunga ubukana bw'icyorezo no gukwirakwira kwacyo, no gukora ubushakashatsi mu nzego z'igihugu n'amasomo n'inama, no gukora igenzura ry'umurimo wo kwisuzuma ku rwego rw'intara n'umujyi, harimo mu mijyi no mu cyaro. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangiye gutangaza ko isi ifite gahunda yo gukora ubushakashatsi ku buryo yakwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus, ndetse no kuvuga uburyo igihugu gishobora gukora mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Mu gusubiza ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi ba ONU muri Irani kugira ngo barebe uko ibintu bimeze. Ku rwego rw'icyorezo ku isi, abasirikare ba OMS bavuze ko urwego rw'akaga rushobora kuzamuka ruva kuri 10 ku ijana kugeza kuri 10 ku ijana, kandi ko ari rwo ruri hejuru mu rwego rw'ibyavuzwe n'ibyavuzwe.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka igera kuri mirongo itatu, abantu benshi batangiye kujya mu mihango yo kwibuka umunsi mukuru w'abakobwa, ariko nyuma y'aho, batangiye kujya mu mihango yo kwibuka abakobwa.
"Virusi iri mu nzira yayo, kandi ugomba kwitegura"" asaba ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ""ibihe bibi cyane".
Ryan yongeyeho ko amakuru ariho ubu adahagije kugira ngo abategetsi b'ubuzima rusange batangaze ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi, kandi ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo ari ugushidikanya ko abantu bose ku isi bazaterwa n'iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS ihangayikishijwe cyane n'uko ubwandu n'uburemere bigeze ku rwego rukomeye, ndetse n'uko umubare w'abanduye ukomeje kuba hasi cyane. OMS yanenzwe cyane kubera ko itakoze ibishoboka byose mu kugenzura icyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange no gutinda gutangaza virusi nk'icyorezo.
Mu bitekerezo by'ibyihebe harimo n'ibisabwa ku wa 6 Mata byo kwegura kwa Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, byashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri ONU zashimangiye ko hakenewe kwita ku burenganzira bwa muntu bw'umuntu ku giti cye muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke rivuga ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira icyo akora ngo akize ubuzima bwe, kandi ko Leta ari yo igomba kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba na rimwe kuba impamvu yo gutandukanya abantu.
Impuguke zemeza ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga n'abafite ubumuga, abantu bo mu moko mato, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi zitagira aho ziba, abatagira aho baba, abakennye cyane, abafite ubumuga bwo kutabona, impunzi n'abandi bantu bataravugwaho rumwe bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga birimo guhangana n'ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubufatanye mu by'ubukungu n'iterambere ryashyizeho urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru mu gihe nyacyo kandi yuzuye, ariko kandi no gutanga ibitekerezo n'ibitekerezo ku miyoborere yo gusubiza mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi.
Kuva ku gushyiraho politiki yo gukomeza sisitemu z'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'ifungwa n'imihango yo guhagarika ingendo, ikigo cya digitale kirimo uburyo bwo kugenzura politiki y'igihugu, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga hamwe no koroshya imikorere y'ibihugu ku kibazo cya coronavirus.
Eduardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil, Michel Gorff, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Bwongereza, na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bashinja leta y'u Bushinwa uburyo yakemuye icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya Ebola cyadutse mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi benshi bo ku rwego rw'intara b'ishyaka rya gikomunisti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) barirukanywe kubera uburyo bakemuye ibibazo by'ubwirinzi mu bice by'ibanze by'Ubushinwa, ikimenyetso cy'uko inzego za politiki zitishimiye uko zitabiriye icyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko iki gikorwa kigamije kurinda Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa (urugero nka Zhao Lijian) banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyaturutse i Wuhan, bakomeza kuvuga ko COVID-19 ishobora kuba yatangiriye muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Guverinoma ya Amerika ya Donald Trump yavuze ko coronavirus ari virusi y'u Bushinwa cyangwa Wuhan, avuga ko kuba Ubushinwa bwagabanyije amakuru byatumye virusi iba icyorezo ku isi.
"Ibintu byose ku Bushinwa" byashyizwe ahagaragara n'ubuyobozi bwa Amerika, buvuga ko hari ingamba z'itumanaho zashyizweho mu nama y'umutekano y'igihugu i Daleb.
"Twabwiwe ko tugomba gukwirakwiza ubu butumwa hakoreshejwe uburyo bwose bushoboka, harimo ibiganiro n'ibiganiro bya televiziyo"" Amakuru dukesha Politico, Politiki y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga na Bloomberg avuga ko kugerageza kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'imyidagaduro yo kwigarurira isi".
"Umuyobozi w'ishami ry'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga, José Boyer, yaburiye ko hari "ubunyangamugayo" mu mishinga yo gushaka kugira uruhare mu nzego za politiki no mu ntego za politiki".
Borrel yavuze ko Ubushinwa bufite inshingano zitandukanye n'iza Amerika, kandi ko bufite imbaraga zo gushishikariza igihugu cyabo kuba inshuti yiringirwa.
Mu gihe Ubushinwa buha inkunga Venezuela na Irani, yasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran.
Ibi birego by'ibanga by'ibanga byatanzwe na Jack Ma kuri Cuba byahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Mata kubera ibihano bya Amerika.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka igera kuri mirongo itatu, leta ya Amerika yashinje leta zunze ubumwe z'Amerika ko zagiye zinyuza mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, zigamije gusa gushimisha ibihugu by'amahanga.
