Mu gihe cy'imyaka igera kuri mirongo itatu, mu bihugu byinshi, abantu benshi batunze amatungo y'inkazi, ariko hari n'abafite ubumuga bwo kutabona.
Ibizamini byo mu mavuriro bya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano n'indwara ya coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) birimo uburyo bwo kumenya aho virusi iherereye no kumenya udukoko tw'umubiri dutanga ibisubizo ku cyorezo.
RT-PCR, ikora ubushakashatsi ku cyitwa RNA cya koronavirusi, yemeje ko abarwayi bafite virusi.
Iki kizamini cyateguwe by'umwihariko kugirango kigaragare gusa kuri RNA ya SARS-CoV-2.
Hari ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa vuba cyangwa bukiri muzima.
Kubona udukoko tw'umubiri (plasma) birashobora gukoreshwa mu gupima no gukwirakwiza mu baturage.
Ibizamini by'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu bamaze kwandura iyi ndwara, harimo abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo bidashobora gutangwa cyangwa abatarayigaragaza.
Ibipimo by'iyi miti bishobora gutuma hagaragara umubare nyawo w'abapfa n'uko ubwirinzi bw'abantu bungana.
Kubera ko nta gihugu na kimwe cyatangaje amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira rya virusi mu baturage bacyo kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, kubera ko hari imikorere y'ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyakoze ibizamini birenze 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi imibare y'ibizamini byakozwe mu bihugu byinshi iratandukanye cyane.
Ibi bitekerezo by'uko abantu benshi bapfa kubera indwara z'ibicurane, byerekana ko hari abantu benshi bapfa kubera indwara z'ibicurane, ariko hari n'abandi benshi bapfa kubera indwara z'ibicurane.
Ikoreshwa ry'ubuhanga bwo kuvura imikorere ya polymeres mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR) isuzuma ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byakozwe mu buryo butandukanye, harimo urugero rw'umutsi wo mu mazuru cyangwa urw'umunyu.
Ubusanzwe, ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa se iminsi ibiri.
Ibipimo bya RT-PCR byakozwe ku matembabuzi y'umuhogo ni byo byiringirwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha, ikagenda ikura mu muhogo.
Mu cyumweru cya kabiri, abanduye bashobora gupima ibipimo bakoresheje umugozi wo mu nda cyangwa se bakoresheje umugozi wo mu muhogo.
Muri Mutarama 2020, ikigo cya Charité i Berlin cyakoze igerageza rya mbere rya PCR rikoresheje uburyo bwo gufotora mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR) hakoreshejwe imikorere ya polymeresic chain reverse transcription (rRT-PCR), maze hatangwa ibikoresho 250,000 by'igerageza byatanzwe n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
United Kingdom na yo yagaragaje ibizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech cyashyize ahagaragara ibikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR ku rwego rw'ubuvuzi ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Ni cyo gikoresho cya mbere mu Bushinwa, BGI Group, cyahawe uruhushya n'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'imiti cy'Ubushinwa (Chinese National Medicinal Goods Administration) rwo gukoresha mu buryo bw'ibanze ibikoresho by'igerageza bya SARS-CoV-2 bishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatanze ikoranabuhanga ryo gupima RT-PCR ya coronavirus (2019-nCoV) mu gihe nyacyo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi rusange binyuze mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga mpuzamahanga.
Ibipimo bya kera byagenewe gupima ADN, kimwe muri bitatu, byakozwe mu buryo bwo guhimba imiti, ndetse n'ibipimo by'umuhogo w'amacupa muri CDC i Atlanta, byatumye ibisubizo bitagera kuri bose. Muri Gashyantare 2020, ku munsi, ku munsi, ku kigero cy'ibimenyetso by'uruhu, byakozwe ku munsi, nta na 100 byakozwe neza.
Ibipimo by'ibikoresho bibiri ntibyashoboraga kwemezwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, bituma ibigo by'ubushakashatsi bya leta n'ibyaho byemererwa gutangira ibizamini.
Ibizamini byemejwe n'ubuyobozi bw'ibiribwa n'imiti ku bw'uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu bihe by'ubukangurambaga. Ibizamini byatangiye mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020 muri laboratwari z'ubucuruzi muri Amerika.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko ibizamini bishingiye kuri RT-PCR bya COVID-19 byamaze kuboneka mu gihugu hose.
Quest Diagnostics yakoze nk'ibyo kugira ngo ibizamini bya COVID-19 byemezwe mu gihugu hose ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta mbogamizi z'umubare zatangajwe, ariko gukusanya no gukora ibizamini by'uruhu bizakorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, igerageza rya COVID-19 ryakozwe n'ikigo cya Leta gishinzwe ubushakashatsi mu by'imikorere ya virusi n'ikoranabuhanga (VECTOR).
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ibizamini byanditswe na Federal Service for Post-Immunization in Healthcare. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko yagaragaje ibizamini byo gusuzuma icyorezo cya COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yabonye uruhushya rwa FDA ku igerageza rimwe, rigomba gukorwa mu mibare myinshi mu masaha 3.5, ku buryo buri mashini ishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uburenganzira bwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa kuri Laboratwari za Abbott kugirango zikore ibizamini bya sisitemu ya m2000 ya Abbott. Mbere yaho, FDA yari yahaye uburenganzira nk'ubwo Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Cepheid na yo yahawe uruhushya rw'ubutabazi (EUA) na FDA ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe 2020 ku buryo bw'igerageza ryamaze iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikoranabuhanga rya isomeric nucleic acid technology mu cyimbo cya PCR.
Ibi ntibikeneye guhuza ibisabwa by'ingendo z'ubushyuhe zihindagurika, ariko ubu buryo butanga ibisubizo byiza muminota itanu n'ibisubizo by'ingaruka mbi muminota 13.
Muri iki gihe, muri Amerika hari imashini zigera ku 18,000, kandi Abbott yiteze kongera inganda ku buryo ishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 50,000 ku munsi. Igerageza rikoresha umubiri wa monoclonal wunganira cyane cyane poroteyine ya N ya coronavirus nshya ririmo gukorwa muri Taiwan, ryitezwe gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'igikorwa cyo gupima ibicurane byihuse.
Igitekerezo cyo muri Werurwe 2020 cyerekana ko ibimenyetso by'ibimenyetso bya Kiriniki bifite agaciro gake mu gupima mu byiciro bya mbere, mu gihe ibimenyetso bya CT (Computer Tomography) bishobora kuba mbere y'uko ibimenyetso biboneka.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe kuri CT harimo iboneka ry'ibumba ryinshi ku mpande zombi, aho nta kwihuza ku mpande, ariko hakurikiraho gusaranganya.
Mu gihe indwara igenda irushaho gutera imbere, habaho imikorere y'ubutegetsi bw'igitugu, imyanya y'icyubahiro n'ubwiyunge.
Nubwo ubushakashatsi bwagereranyije PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho icyorezo cyugarije isi, bufite uburemere buke, ibimenyetso byabyo birasubiramo ibindi bimenyetso by'umusonga n'ubundi burwayi, kandi CT ishobora kwerekana neza kurusha PCR.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe iby'Imihango cyagiraga inama ko CT idakwiye gukoreshwa nk'igikorwa cya mbere cyo gupima COVID-19 cyangwa icy'ubushakashatsi. Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yagiriye inama PCR nk'igikorwa cya mbere cyo gupima.
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku ndwara ni ugukora udukoko tw'umubiri, harimo IgM na IgG.
Abantu bafite iminsi 7 cyangwa irengaho bagaragaza ibimenyetso, bashobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu, gupima ubwirinzi no kugenzura abantu. Ibipimo bishobora gukorerwa mu ma laboratwari nkuru (CLT) cyangwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi (PoCT).
Nubwo hari ibipimo byinshi by'ibikoresho byikora mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bishobora gukora ibi bipimo, ubushobozi bwabyo buzaterwa n'uburyo buri buryo butanga ibisubizo.
Nubwo ingero z'ibinure zishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, akenshi ikoreshwa mu cyiciro kimwe cy'amaraso mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi bw'ibinyabuzima.
Mu gihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina, umuntu ashobora guhita atangira gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, ntabwo bisaba ko hashyirwaho icyiciro cyo gukuramo mbere yo gukora ibizamini. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yagaragaje imiryango 29 yamenyesheje ikigo, ubu ikaba ishobora gutanga ibizamini by'umubiri.
Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, FDA yemeje ibizamini byonyine mu buryo bwemewe bwo gukoresha mu bihe by'ubukonje. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics n'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya Epitope Diagnostics byemerewe n'inzego z'ubumwe bw'Uburayi ku bikoresho byabyo by'ubushakashatsi, bishobora gusuzuma IgG na IgA z'abandura virusi mu maraso y'abantu.
Kubera ko ishobora gupima ibipimo amagana mu masaha make, PCR ni vuba cyane kurusha gupima virusi ya RNA.
Ubusanzwe, udukoko tw'umubiri twigaragaza mu minsi 14 uhereye igihe ubwandu bwatangiriye. Ubwongereza bwabonye ibikoresho by'igerageza by'indwara z'umubiri by'umubiri bwaguze mu ntangiriro za Mata bitagikora neza.
Hong Kong yashyizeho uburyo bwo gutuma abarwayi bakekwa kuguma mu rugo. Urwego rw'ubutabazi ruzaha umurwayi icyuma cy'ibirahuri cy'uruhu. Bashyiramo umunyu, bagasubiramo, hanyuma ingaruka zikaza nyuma y'igihe gito. NHS yo mu Bwongereza yatangaje ko uburyo bwo gupima abarwayi bakekwa mu rugo ari ubwa mbere, aho birinda indwara zandura abandi mu gihe umurwayi ageze mu bitaro kandi agakoresha ambulansi.
Ibigo by'ibizamini by'abashoferi bifasha Koreya y'Epfo kubona ibizamini byihuse kandi byimbitse kurusha ibindi bihugu byose. Mu Budage, itsinda ry'abaganga b'ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bw'ibanze ryavuze ku wa 2 Werurwe ko bashobora gukora ibizamini 12.000 ku munsi mu byiciro by'abari mu kato, ugereranyije n'ibizamini 10.700 byakozwe mu cyumweru gishize.
Iyo muganga agutegetse gukora ikizamini, amafaranga y'ubwishingizi aba ari yo akurikizwa.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi w'ikigo Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 160,000 buri cyumweru.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, ibizamini by'imodoka mu mijyi myinshi byatangiye.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzwi kuko hatangajwe gusa ibipimo by'ubwandu.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwa laboratwari bwakozwe mu cyumweru cya 12/2020, aho hagaragaye ibipimo 33,491 bya SARS-CoV-2 (6.9%) n'ibipimo 483,295 by'ibihimba by'umubiri. Abashakashatsi mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam muri Isiraheli bagerageje uburyo bwo gupima ibipimo 64 by'abarwayi icyarimwe. Ibimenyetso by'ibipimo byakusanyijwe, hanyuma ibindi bizakorwa ari uko gusa ibipimo byakusanyijwe byerekana ko byanduye.
Iyi moderi yateguwe mu minsi itanu, iyobowe n'uwashinze BGI, Wang Jian, ivuga ko niba ubushobozi bwo gupima butakoreshwa, ubwandu bwa Hubei bushobora kwiyongeraho 47%, kandi igiciro cyo guhangana n'ingendo zo mu ngendo gishobora kwiyongera kabiri.
Ibi bitaro bya Wuhan, hamwe n'ibitaro bya Huawei muri Shanxi, Tianjin, Beijing na Shanghai, byahise bikurikira mu mijyi 12 yo mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, ibizamini bya buri munsi byibura 50,000 ku munsi. Ni umurongo ukingutse kandi ibyinshi muri byo byakozwe mu buryo buciriritse, imashini ikorwa na Origami Assays ishobora gupima COVID-19 ku bipimo by'uruhu by'abarwayi 1122 mu munsi umwe ikoresheje impapuro 93 gusa.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, icyatumye EU, UK na USA bigira ibizamini byinshi ni uko nta bikoresho bihagije by'ibikoresho.
Ibi byatumye bamwe mu banditsi bashakisha uburyo bwo gutegura ibipimo, harimo no gushyushya iminota 5 ku gipimo cya 98 °C (208 °F) kugira ngo genome za RNA zigeragerezwe. Ku ya 31 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu (UAE) zatangaje ko ubu zigerageza virusi ya coronavirus ku muntu umwe mu baturage bazo kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose, kandi ko zigiye kugera ku rwego rwo kugera ku bantu benshi.
Ibi byose byakozwe n'itsinda rya 42 ry'abakora mu muhanda, hamwe na BGI (Ikigo cyabo cy'Ubushobozi bwo Gushakisha Ibyihutirwa mu Burozi bwa Huo-Yan) mu Bushinwa, mu rwego rwo gukora ibisasu mu bantu benshi.
Iyi laboratwari yatwaye iminsi 14 ngo yubakwe, ikora ibizamini bya RT-PCR ibihumbi 10 ku munsi, ikaba ari laboratwari ya mbere ku isi ikora ibizamini by'uru rwego hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Uburyo butandukanye bwo kugerageza kugenzura ibice bitandukanye bya porogaramu ya virusi ya coronavirus, byakozwe mu Bushinwa, Ubufaransa, Ubudage, Hong Kong, Ubuyapani na Amerika.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze imikorere y'ibikomoka ku Budage mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, nta bikoresho bikenewe kugira ngo bikore.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatinze kubona ibizamini muri Amerika, kandi ntibyari bigishoboka kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, Ubushinwa na Amerika byari bifite ibibazo ku bijyanye n'ubuziranenge bw'ibikoresho by'igerageza, kandi ibyo bihugu na Ositaraliya ntibyashoboraga gutanga ibizamini bihagije hamwe n'ibizamini byemejwe n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima kugeza igihe ibisabwa byuzujwe.
Mu buryo butandukanye, impuguke zivuga ko kuba Koreya y'Epfo ifite uburyo bwinshi bwo gupima bishobora gufasha kugabanya ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya.
Leta ya Koreya y'Epfo imaze imyaka myinshi yubaka ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini, cyane cyane mu bigo byigenga.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Umuryango Mpuzamahanga wita ku Buzima washishikarije kongerera imbaraga gahunda zo gupima nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ikibazo cy'ubunyangamugayo mu bikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Mu gihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, CDC yakoze ibizamini by'ibinyabutabire by'ubwoko butandukanye, harimo ibipimo by'ibinyabutabire by'ubwoko butandukanye. Nyuma y'aho, leta yakuyeho inzitizi z'ubutegetsi zabuzaga abantu gukora ibizamini by'ibanze.
