Ibipimo, kugenzura abantu banduye no gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 byagize ingaruka nziza.
Abashakashatsi bakorera mu mujyi wa Vo mu Butaliyani, aho habereye urupfu rwa mbere rw'umuntu wahitanywe na COVID-19, bakoze ibizamini by'ubwandu inshuro ebyiri mu gihe cy'iminsi icumi, ku baturage bagera ku 3400.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abakoze ibizamini nta bimenyetso by'indwara bagaragaje, kandi abanduye bose bari mu kato.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka igera kuri mirongo itatu, umubare munini w'abanduye ukomeje kwiyongera.
Gukurikirana cyane, gupima no kwigunga byerekana ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cya 2020 muri Singapuru cyandukira gahoro cyane kurusha ibindi bihugu byateye imbere, bidasaba ko habaho gufunga cyane amazu yo kuriramo n'amaduka.
Nubwo ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, Singapore yahagaritse ibikorwa byinshi by'imyidagaduro, ndetse n'abaturage barakangurirwa kuguma mu ngo zabo, amashuri yongeye gufungura ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nyuma y'iminsi mikuru.
Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho ingamba zikomeye mu gucunga icyorezo, kugabanya ingendo zinjira mu gihugu no gushyira mu kato, ariko ntabwo byashyizeho ingamba zikomeye mu guhagarika, urugero nka Isilande na Koreya y'Epfo.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byakoze ibizamini byinshi bifite umubare muto w'abapfa, wenda kubera ko ibihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo kubona ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa bidahari.
OMS yasabye ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima na laboratwari z'igihugu zifite ubunararibonye ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 kohereza ibipimo bitanu bya mbere byanduye na 10 bya mbere bitanduye bya COVID-19 kuri kimwe mu bigo 16 by'ubushakashatsi byashyizweho na OMS kugira ngo byemezwe.
Muri ibi byumba 16, 7 biri muri Aziya, 5 biri mu Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika ya Ruguru na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Dore urutonde rw'abantu banduye mu bipimo by'ubwandu byakozwe n'ingamba z'igihugu.
Igihugu kigenzura gusa abarwayi bari mu bitaro, cyaba gifite ibimenyetso cyangwa kitagaragaza, mu bindi bintu byose, kirangana n'ibindi bihugu bigenzura abaturage bose, ariko ku kigero cyo hejuru, igipimo cy'ubwandu kizaba kiri hejuru.
Gukaraba intoki, nanone bizwi nka sanitizer y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki z'umuntu ku giti cye, hagamijwe gukuraho imyanda, amavuta, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe runaka cy'umunsi, cyane cyane mu gihe cy'amasaha y'ikiruhuko, bifasha kwirinda indwara nyinshi zandura, urugero nk'indwara z'ibicurane n'indwara z'ibicurane.
Abantu batameshe intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, amazuru n'umunwa (urushinge rw'umwanda) bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane.
Igihe cy'ingenzi cyo gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabuni mu munsi ni mbere yo kujya mu bwiherero, nyuma yo guhindura imyenda y'imbere cyangwa impapuro z'ibanga, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa mbere yo gukora ku nyama zitagifite intungamubiri, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje ivu.
Mbere yo gutegura ibyokurya, mu gihe cyo kubitegura no nyuma yo kubitegura.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura imashini cyangwa gusukura umwana ukiri muto.
Iyo umuntu amaze gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa gukorora, ashobora guhita yumva ko ari we wenyine ufite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibyo ashaka.
Iyo uhuye n'inyamaswa, ibyokurya cyangwa imyanda y'inyamaswa.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi yerekeza ku myitozo y'isuku y'ibidukikije ifitanye isano n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gufata imiti cyangwa mbere yo kujya kwa muganga bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ubwandu.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ukugabanya ubwandu bw'ibicurane (bakteriya, virusi cyangwa ibindi bikoko bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'ubumara bishobora guteza indwara cyangwa se bishobora gutera indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora akazi ko gufata amafunguro cyangwa mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bishobora kugira akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ubwandu bw'ibicurane, virusi ya corona n'izindi ndwara zandura, gukumira indwara z'ibicurane, no kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Nyuma y'ibyo, umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cy'amabyiruka mu ngo ni muto.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko kongera imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu bagira uburambe mu mikurire.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, impfu z'abana ziterwa n'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'iz'inkondo y'umura, zishobora kugabanywa hifashishijwe ibintu byoroheje byo mu myitwarire nko gukoresha isabune no gukaraba intoki.
