Hari ibindi byinshi bikeneye gukorwa mu rwego rwo kumenya uburyo bwiza bwo kuvura mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, isabune n'isabune mu ntoki ni uburyo buhendutse kandi bw'ingenzi bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza no kugira imirire myiza.
Ariko, kubura amazi, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo, mu mashuri no ku kazi bishobora gutuma gukaraba intoki bitoroha ku isi hose.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro muri Afurika, hari uburyo bworoshye bwo kubaka imisarani y'amaboko, ariko usanga imisarani y'amaboko ari nke cyane hafi y'ubwiherero bwite cyangwa rusange.
Ariko kandi, kuba abantu bataraba bakaraba intoki, ahanini biterwa n'imyitwarire yabo isanzwe aho guterwa n'ibura ry'amazi n'isabune.
Gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ifatwa, bigatuma abantu barushaho kumenya ibyiza byo gukaraba intoki, kandi bishobora gutuma abantu benshi bahindura imyitwarire.
Kugira ngo ikore neza, ikeneye kugenzurwa no gusuzumwa.
Isuzuma ry'igikorwa cya 70 ryagaragaje ko mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ay'igiciro cy'ubudehe, uburyo bwo gukora bushingiye ku baturage bwagize akamaro mu gukwirakwiza ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki, mu gihe gahunda zo gucuruza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga ziteze imbere. Urugero rumwe rwo kuzamura ibikorwa byo gukaraba intoki mu mashuri, ni uburyo bw'ishuri rya UNICEF bwo gushishikariza abanyeshuri gukoresha uburyo bworoshye kandi buhendutse mu ishuri bwo gukaraba intoki neza n'isabune.
Amashuri ashobora guhinduka kuva ku nyenyeri imwe kugeza ku nyenyeri eshatu, iyo yujuje ibipimo by'ibanze.
Kubaka ahantu ho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga w'Amazi ni urugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo kwimakaza ubushishozi bugamije guhindura imyitwarire. UNICEF yashyigikiye ikoreshwa ry'amashusho y'amaboko mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwagaragaje ko kugabanya amafaranga yo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere binyuze mu kwirinda DALY.
Ariko, hari igitekerezo cy'uko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo bihenze cyane ugereranyije n'ibindi bikorwa byo gukaraba amazi n'isuku.
Igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'umuntu, cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere igoranye, urugero nk'ababyeyi bakiri bato cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse bari mu bitaro, cyamenyekanye bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'umuganga w'Umuhungari wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, Ignaz Semmelweis, n'Umwongereza Florence Nightingale washinze ubuforomo bw'iki gihe.
Abantu benshi bakomeje kwizera ko ubwandu bwa mbere bwagaragaye ari ubwandu bw'impumuro mbi, bita miasmas.
Mu myaka ya 1980, icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ziterwa n'ibiribwa n'indwara z'ibyorezo ziterwa n'ubuzima byatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitera inkunga cyane isuku y'amaboko nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyabaye mu 2009 na COVID-19 mu 2020, byatumye abantu benshi mu bihugu byinshi bamenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura nk'izo.
Urugero, mu Budage, mu byumba by'ubwogero bya rubanda no mu mazu y'ibiro, ndetse no ku bibuga by'indege, hari ibishushanyo byanditseho uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki, biri iruhande rw'ubwiherero.
Mu magambo y'umwimerere, ijambo "gukaraba intoki" risobanura ko umuntu adashaka kugira uruhare cyangwa uruhare mu kintu runaka.
Iyi mvugo yaturutse ku murongo wo muri Matayo, aho Ponsiyo Pilato yoza intoki ze igihe yafataga umwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu, ariko yaje gukoreshwa cyane mu ndimi zimwe na zimwe z'icyongereza.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki cyane mu rwego rwo gusukura ishusho y'ibyiyumvo by'ibyaha yakoze, no mu rwego rwo kugerageza gusukura ishusho y'ibyaha byashishikarije umugabo we kubikora, agaragaza ko azi icyaha yakoze.
Abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki kenshi kurusha abandi, kandi bakishimira ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki cyane nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku myitwarire itemewe.
Ikindi kandi, abantu bafite imyumvire nk'iyo kandi bakaba bashobora gukaraba intoki nyuma, usanga batitabira ibikorwa by'isuku by'ubundi buryo, urugero nko gukora ubwitange.
Amadini amwe n'amwe asaba ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu buryo bw'isuku no mu buryo bw'imihango. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'imihango, ukoresheje amazi gusa cyangwa isabune, ni uburyo bukoreshwa mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Bahá'í, idini ry'Abahindu, idini rya Twila n'iry'Abayahudi, idini rya Laotian, idini rya Laotian n'iry'Abisilamu.
Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abisiramu bigisha ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero.
Ikindi kandi, Abahindu, Ababuda, Abasikikimu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu basabwa gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma y'ifunguro.
Ubuyobozi bw'Akarere ka Gasabo:
Kugabanya ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni ugukoresha uburyo bwo kwirinda ibyago byo mu kazi, umutekano n'ubuzima mu kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura neza aho bakorera bishingiye ku igenzura ry'ibyago by'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga ku kazi n'intego z'akazi, ubukana bw'uburwayi mu baturage n'ibintu bishobora guteza akaga ku bakozi ku giti cyabo bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi (OSHA) kivuga ko imirimo irimo abantu benshi ariko ikagira uruhare ruto mu guhura n'abandi bakozi, ari yo ifite ibyago bike byo kwandura, kandi ko inama z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zirimo gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo gukorora no gukorora, no gukora isuku isanzwe mu kazi.
Ibikorwa bishobora guteza ubwandu mu buryo buhagije, birimo ibikorwa bisaba ko umuntu aba hafi cyangwa kenshi n'abantu batazi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, hamwe n'ibikorwa bishobora kuba byatewe n'ubwandu bw'abantu benshi cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri bo harimo abakozi bahura n'abaturage muri rusange, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo myinshi, hamwe n'ahandi hari ibicuruzwa byinshi.
Usibye ibikorwa by'ibanze byo kwirinda indwara zandura, kugenzura ibyago by'iki cyiciro harimo guhumeka mu buryo bw'umwuka hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'isuku bikora neza, kurinda guhumeka, no kuba ufite ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe ari ngombwa kuvugana n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi cyangwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi by'umutima bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, kandi ko bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, cyangwa abakozi bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'uruhu ku bantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, cyangwa bakora ibikorwa byo gutunganya udusimba duturuka mu kirere.
Mu by'ukuri, mu gihe umuntu akoresha ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi, ashobora kubona ko nta cyo bitwaye.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gifite ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kudakora bitewe n'uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa impungenge z'uko bashobora guhura n'ibiza.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka haba mu bicuruzwa bikenewe ndetse n'uburyo biboneka (urugero: kugura mu gihe cy'iminota myinshi, cyangwa gutanga ibicuruzwa ku nzu cyangwa serivisi zo kugura imodoka).
Amaherezo, ibicuruzwa biva mu turere tw'icyaro aho COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye cyane bishobora gutinda. Gutegura no gukemura indwara zandura bishobora gukoreshwa nk'icyitegererezo cy'ibikorwa byo kwirinda.
Imishinga ifata ingamba zo guhangana n'ibikomoka ku mitungo, harimo ibyago byugarije ahantu hakorerwa imirimo itandukanye n'intego z'ubucuruzi, ibyago bituruka ku miterere y'inzu n'abaturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Zanavuga uburyo bwo kugenzura kugira ngo haboneke ibisubizo by'ibi byago, kandi zishobora no gushyiraho ingamba z'inyongera ku bibazo bishobora kuvuka bitewe n'icyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza icyorezo byateganyijwe hakurikijwe inama zatanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa urw'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, kubungabunga ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bikorwa ku nzira zabo z'itangwa ry'ibikoresho.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ikorerwa bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo by'ibikorwa.
Gushyira mu byiciro uburyo bwo kugenzura akaga ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi n'ubuzima bw'akazi mu rwego rwo gushyira mu byiciro uburyo bwo kugenzura akaga hakurikijwe uko bukora.
Iyo nta bushobozi bwo gukuraho ibyago bya COVID-19 buhari, uburyo bwo kugenzura neza ni ubuhanga, hanyuma hakurikiraho uburyo bwo kugenzura, hanyuma hakagira ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite.
Igenzura ryubwubatsi rikubiyemo gutandukanya abakozi kubyago bijyanye nakazi, hatagombye gushingira kubikorwa byumukozi, kandi birashobora kuba igisubizo gihenze cyane cyo gushyira mubikorwa.
Ubuyobozi bufite ububasha bwo guhindura politiki cyangwa imikorere y'akazi umukozi cyangwa umukoresha asabwa gukora.
Nubwo ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bitagira ingufu nk'uko bigenzurwa mu bwubatsi cyangwa mu buryo bwo gutunganya ibintu, bishobora gufasha mu kurinda abantu guhura n'ibintu runaka.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku ngaruka z'akazi ziterwa n'umukozi, bigakoreshwa neza (urugero: imifuka yo guhumeka), bikambara neza kandi mu buryo buhuje n'imiterere, bigakora igenzura buri gihe, bigakoreshwa mu buryo bukenewe, bigasimbuzwa, bikurwaho neza, bikanahanagurwa, hanyuma bigasubikwa cyangwa bikatwarwa nta nkomyi.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi, ni ko gafite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu benshi.
Ibikorwa by'ibanze byo kwirinda indwara zandura byasabwe ku kazi kose birimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo umunsi utameze neza, gupfuka ubwonko n'ubuhumekero, guhanagura imyanda no gushyira imyanda aho ikwiye, kwitegura guhanahana amakuru cyangwa gutandukanya aho bakorera, kubuza abakozi gukoresha izindi gahunda n'ibikoresho, gukomeza gukora isuku isanzwe ku kazi no mu bidukikije no kuzirinda indwara.
Gushakisha vuba no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kuba banduye ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi bantu ku kazi.
Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kiratera inkunga abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zitunguranye, kuguma mu rugo kugeza nibura amasaha 24 nta burwayi, ubushyuhe, ibimenyetso by'umuriro mwinshi, n'ibindi bimenyetso, nta miti ya malaria cyangwa imiti ihindura ibimenyetso, no kugira ngo politiki yo kuruhuka mu gihe urwaye ihinduke, abakozi bagume mu rugo bita ku bagize umuryango barwaye, kandi bashishikarize abakozi kumenya neza politiki yayo.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, abakozi bakunze guhura cyangwa kugirana imishyikirano ya bugufi n'abarwayi bakekwaho COVID-19 cyangwa abandi bantu batazi bari mu ntera ya metero esheshatu (1,8 m) ni bo bafite ibyago byo kwandura SARS-CoV-2. Ariko, umuntu ashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 kubera ko ashobora kuba aherutse gukora urugendo mu gihugu mu karere ka COVID-19 kari gafite ubwandu, aho umurwayi akora ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi.
Muri byo harimo abakozi bagiranye umubano usanzwe n'abaturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo imirimo ituje, no mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubucuruzi buciriritse. Muri ibyo harimo no gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi bifite ingufu nyinshi mu kugenzura umutekano w'abakozi mu matsinda y'ibyago byinshi, gushyiraho ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi bigezweho by'ubwubatsi, guhuza abakozi n'akazi mu buryo bufite ibyago, gutanga amahugurwa cyangwa gahunda zo guhana amakuru ku buzima bw'abakozi, guhuza abakozi n'akazi mu gihe cy'akazi, gutanga amahugurwa cyangwa gahunda zo kwirinda COVID-19, no gutanga ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi n'ibindi bikenewe, nko gutunganya ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku bantu benshi cyane cyane n'amatsinda y'abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura indwara, guhuza abakozi n'ibyago byo mu rugo, no gukemura ibibazo by'uburwayi ku kazi, hamwe no gutanga amahugurwa ku bantu batagira aho bahurira n'akazi, aho gukora cyangwa aho batangira, no gutanga amahugurwa ku bantu batagira aho bahurira n'abandi bantu bakenera kwirinda COVID-19 mu gihe gikenewe.
Abakozi bo muri iki cyiciro cy'abafite ibyago byinshi ntibakunze gukenera gukoresha imashini zo guhumeka.
Mu rwego rwo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagenzi mu buryo bukwiriye mu gihe umuntu arwaye mu ndege, harimo kurinda umuntu urwaye kujya kure y'abandi ku burebure bwa metero 6, guha umukozi w'indege kwita ku muntu urwaye, no guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa mu gihe yitsamura cyangwa anuka, cyangwa kumusaba ko yambara umwenda w'umunyandiko mu maso no mu kanwa.
Abagize abakozi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara intoki z'ubuvuzi zishobora gukoreshwa igihe bahuye n'ibintu bishobora kwanduza cyangwa imyanda ituruka ku mubiri, cyangwa igihe bakorera abagenzi barwaye. Iyo bishoboka, abakozi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye mu gihe babonye ibimenyetso by'uburwayi cyangwa guhora bakorora cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bikoresho bikoreshwa rimwe bigomba gushyirwa mu mifuka yo kurinda ibyago, hanyuma ibintu byose byanduye bigakorwaho isuku no gukaraba. Ku mato y'ubucuruzi, harimo amato y'ubunini n'andi mato y'abashyitsi, ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago zirimo gutinda urugendo mu gihe cy'uburwayi, kwigunga no kwiherera, no guhita bamenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu bwato mu gihe cy'ubwato, ubushyuhe bukabije n'ibindi bimenyetso by'uburwayi.
CDC irasaba ko amashuri n'amazu y'abana bazajya bavurirwa mu gihe gito kugira ngo bisukure cyangwa byandure, niba hari umuntu wanduye wigeze kwinjira mu kigo cy'ishuri, yaba yanduye mu baturage cyangwa atari yo.
Mu gihe hari ubwandu buke cyangwa buciriritse, hari uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu, nko kujya mu ngendo zo mu mirima, guterana no guterana mu buryo bw'umubiri cyangwa amahugurwa yo kuririmba, cyangwa guteranira hamwe mu nzu y'ibiro, kongera umwanya hagati y'ameza, gutegura igihe cyo kugera n'igihe cyo kuva, kugabanya abashyitsi b'ingenzi, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho kwita ku buzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bisa na COVID.
Mu gihe hari ubwandu bwinshi mu baturage, ingamba zo gutandukanya abantu zishobora gutekerezwa, kimwe no kongera igihe cyo gufunga amashuri. CDC ivuga ko nta ngaruka ku buzima bw'inzego zishinzwe kubahiriza amategeko zikora imirimo isanzwe ya buri munsi.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakunze guhura n'abantu bagaragayeho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye COVID-19 basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ibanze, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye.
Iyo habaye guhura kwa hafi mu gihe cy'ibihe by'imvura, abakozi bagomba gusukura no guhanagura imifuka yabo n'ibikoresho byabo bakoresheje imyanda yo mu rugo cyangwa imyenda yo gukaraba mbere yo kongera kubikoresha, hanyuma bakagendera ku mabwiriza yo gushyira no kujugunya ibikoresho bya bwite bikoreshwa, no gushyira no kwirukana imyenda.
OSHA ivuga ko hari abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi bw'ibihaha bafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi byo kwandura.
Ibikorwa birimo ibyago byinshi birimo gutanga ubuvuzi, gutanga serivisi, gukora ibizamini no gutwara abarwayi, ndetse n'abakozi bo mu by'ubuvuzi bahuye n'abantu bazi cyangwa bakeka ko banduye COVID-19.
Iyo abakozi bakusanya cyangwa bagakoresha utuntu duto cyane ku bantu bazi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, bishobora kuba byateza ibyago byinshi.
Uburyo bwo gutwara utwo duce mu kirere, harimo gutwara imyanda, kugabanya ubukana bw'isukari, kureba mu muyoboro w'ubuhumekero, gukora ibizamini by'amenyo cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'uruhu rw'umubiri.
Ibikorwa byo kubaga umutima bifite ibyago byinshi birimo abakozi bakora mu gutunganya imirambo y'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19 igihe bapfaga. Iyo bakoze ibizamini byo kubaga umutima, baba bafite ibyago byinshi. Nanone, bakora ibikorwa by'ubwubatsi by'inyongera ku matsinda y'abarwayi bafite ibyago, harimo n'ibikorwa byo guhanga udusimba duturuka mu kirere, harimo n'ibyumba by'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19.
Imikorere y'ubushyuhe bw'umwuka mu kirere bw'ibanze ikoreshwa mu bigo bimwe na bimwe byita ku buzima n'ibyumba bihumanya.
Ibipimo by'uruhu bigomba gukorerwa mu rwego rwa 3 rw'umutekano.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi bagaruka mu gihugu bazajya mu byumba by'igendereza, bitewe n'uko bakekwaho/batakekwaho COVID-19. OSHA yasabye ko abantu bakekwaho cyangwa bakekwaho kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 bagakoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka, kandi bagakora mu kirere kiri hagati y'ibirometero 6 n'abarwayi, cyangwa bagakora imikorere y'ubuhumekero, nko kwinjiza imashini mu mubiri.
Mu rwego rwo gukora gahunda yuzuye yo kwirinda guhumeka muri Amerika, irimo ibizamini by'imikorere, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi, mu gihe mu gihe cyo guhumeka hakoreshwa udupfukamunwa twemewe na NIOSH tw'ibikoresho byo guhumeka cyangwa ibindi birenzeho.
Ubundi buryo bwo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi bugatuma umukozi yumva atuje. COVID-19 ni indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero aho kwandura binyuze mu mazi y'umubiri, bityo OMS ntiyemerera abantu guhumeka bose.
OMS irasaba ko abakozi bavura ku kibuga bakoresha agapfukamunwa ko mu bitaro gusa.
OMS irasaba ko abantu bakira ibipimo by'uruhu rw'ubuhumekero rw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 badafite imikorere y'ibice by'umwuka, cyangwa ngo bitabe ku barwayi cyangwa ngo babitware, bakoresha udupfukamunwa, udushumi cyangwa udupfukamunwa, imyenda n'utugati.
Iyo umuntu akoze ubu buryo bwo guhumeka imyanda mu mwuka, mu cyumba cyo kubaga, asimbuzwa udupfukamunwa two guhumeka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose nta bikoresho bya PPE bihagije, OMS irasaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya umubare w'ibikoresho bya PPE bikoreshwa mu buvuzi hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rigezweho mu itumanaho, ikoreshwa ry'inzitizi zo mu buryo bw'umubiri nka za "transparent windows", abantu bemerewe kwambara gusa mu gihe bari mu cyumba barwariyemo umurwayi wa COVID-19, gukoresha PPE gusa mu bikorwa by'akazi bikenewe, gukoresha ibikoresho bimwe byo guhumeka mu gihe urimo gukurikirana abarwayi benshi bafite indwara imwe, gukurikirana no guhuza ibikoresho bya PPE mu gutanga serivisi, no gushishikariza abantu kudakoresha agapfukamunwa mu gihe badafite ibimenyetso.
