Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ku bufatanye ko bizashyiraho uburyo bwo gukora porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zabo za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije porogaramu ifitanye isano na Alipay, ikora ibijyanye no kureba niba abaturage bashobora guhura n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
